{"word":"στραγγαλίς","slug":"στραγγαλίς","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n97073\" key=\"straggali/s\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">στραγγᾰλ-ίς</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ίδος</itype>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen>, <sense id=\"n97073.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">intricate knot</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0508.tlg001:48\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Stratt.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">48</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὑμεῖς . . ἀεὶ στραγγαλίδας ἐσφίγγετε</foreign> tied <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">knots</tr_> fast (cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">στραγγαλιάω</foreign>), <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0486.tlg001:21\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Pherecr.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">21</biblScope> </bibl>: hence Aristocreon called Chrysippus <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τῶν Ἀκαδημιακῶν στραγγαλίδων κοπίδα</foreign>, a knife to cut Academic <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">knots</tr_>, ap.<bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Plu.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.1033e</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n97073.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">knot</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">induration</tr_> in the breast or other parts, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg014:587b:22\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ HA\">HA</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">587b22</biblScope> </bibl>; cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">στραγγαλιά</foreign>. </sense> <sense n=\"3\" id=\"n97073.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> some kind of ornament, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0527.tlg009:8:26\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ LXX\">LXX</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Jd.\">Jd.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8.26</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ς. ἀργυρᾶ, ς. χρυσᾶ κεκολλημένη</foreign>, <bibl n=\"Perseus:abo:pap,P.Oxy.:1449:18\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ POxy.\">POxy.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1449.18</biblScope></bibl>,<bibl n=\"Perseus:abo:pap,P.Oxy.:23\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">23</biblScope> </bibl> <date TEIform=\"date\">(iii A.D.)</date>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}